{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-programs-js","path":"/programs/domain-verification.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>In order to configure <a href=\"single-sign-on-sso-via-saml.html\">single sign-on via SAML</a>, you need to verify ownership of the domain for your program.</p>\n<p>To verify your domain:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Go to <strong>Program Settings > General > Verified Domains</strong>.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 17.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"verified domains\"\n        title=\"verified domains\"\n        src=\"/static/6eab5249c8412a339fc2855c63e666f1/0b533/verified-domains-1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6eab5249c8412a339fc2855c63e666f1/fac75/verified-domains-1.png 125w,\n/static/6eab5249c8412a339fc2855c63e666f1/63868/verified-domains-1.png 250w,\n/static/6eab5249c8412a339fc2855c63e666f1/0b533/verified-domains-1.png 500w,\n/static/6eab5249c8412a339fc2855c63e666f1/1d69c/verified-domains-1.png 750w,\n/static/6eab5249c8412a339fc2855c63e666f1/00d43/verified-domains-1.png 1000w,\n/static/6eab5249c8412a339fc2855c63e666f1/cd13d/verified-domains-1.png 1958w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>Click <strong>Verify new domain</strong>.</li>\n<li>Choose the <strong>Verification Method</strong> of your domain. You can choose from:</li>\n</ol>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Option</th>\n<th>Details</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>DNS TXT record</td>\n<td>You'll be prompted to add a TXT record to the DNS configuration of your domain to allow HackerOne to verify you have ownership over the domain.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>HTML meta-tag</td>\n<td>You'll be prompted to add an HTML meta-tag to the index page of your domain to allow HackerOne to verify you have ownership over the domain.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Web file</td>\n<td>You'll be prompted to upload a text file to allow HackerOne to verify if you have ownership over the domain.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>Enter the domain name you want to verify in the <strong>Domain name</strong> field.</li>\n<li>Click <strong>Next step</strong>.</li>\n<li>Follow the instructions on the page to allow HackerOne to verify you have ownership over the domain. Instructions will vary depending on the verification method you chose in step 3 above. You'll have to go to your DNS provider to manage settings on the domain.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Here's an example of using the DNS TXT record on Cloudflare to allow HackerOne to verify your domain:</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 42.4%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"domain verification example of using DNS TXT\"\n        title=\"domain verification example of using DNS TXT\"\n        src=\"/static/eea24acbc76f86477d65553b63b38f19/0b533/verified-domains-3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/eea24acbc76f86477d65553b63b38f19/fac75/verified-domains-3.png 125w,\n/static/eea24acbc76f86477d65553b63b38f19/63868/verified-domains-3.png 250w,\n/static/eea24acbc76f86477d65553b63b38f19/0b533/verified-domains-3.png 500w,\n/static/eea24acbc76f86477d65553b63b38f19/1d69c/verified-domains-3.png 750w,\n/static/eea24acbc76f86477d65553b63b38f19/00d43/verified-domains-3.png 1000w,\n/static/eea24acbc76f86477d65553b63b38f19/a6d66/verified-domains-3.png 2070w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"7\">\n<li>Click <strong>Verify</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<p>Once your domain is successfully verified, the status of your domain will be changed to <em>Verified</em>. You can continue to verify your <a href=\"single-sign-on-sso-via-saml.html\">SAML settings</a>.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 24.8%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"verified domains list\"\n        title=\"verified domains list\"\n        src=\"/static/03b21d4bc12a2012db42d27e180759e9/0b533/verified-domains-4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/03b21d4bc12a2012db42d27e180759e9/fac75/verified-domains-4.png 125w,\n/static/03b21d4bc12a2012db42d27e180759e9/63868/verified-domains-4.png 250w,\n/static/03b21d4bc12a2012db42d27e180759e9/0b533/verified-domains-4.png 500w,\n/static/03b21d4bc12a2012db42d27e180759e9/1d69c/verified-domains-4.png 750w,\n/static/03b21d4bc12a2012db42d27e180759e9/00d43/verified-domains-4.png 1000w,\n/static/03b21d4bc12a2012db42d27e180759e9/bcec6/verified-domains-4.png 1834w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>If your verification has failed, you can choose to <strong>Cancel verification</strong></p>","frontmatter":{"path":"/programs/domain-verification.html","id":"programs/domain-verification","title":"Domain Verification","description":null},"headings":[]}},"pageContext":{}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}